<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>134</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thanah A hung kuol hi,
 Hukdampa Isu;
 Ni hung tung ding A ngak,
 Ka Lal Isu.

[V2]
 Than apatin A tho tai,
 Dogal lopi taka zawhna tawh;
 Thim thuneihna apat Guolzo in A tho,
 Mithiengte tawh kumkhuon vaihawm din A hing,
 A tho tai, A tho tai!
 Hallelujah A tho tai.

[V3]
 2. Thawnin than a ngak ui,
 Hukdampa Isu;
 Thawnin a tiemteh ui.
 Ka Lal Isu.

[V4]
 3. Thihnan a tuthei puoi,
 Hukdampa Isu;
 Thihna kanna hih tan,
 Ka Lal Isu'n.</lyrics>
<title>CHRIST AROSE</title>
</song>